</entry><entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>devel_text_visualizer</computeroutput>    </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para>시작 커밋   </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>9970ed2009b9650167398ba5fc935a6d94a84f1f</computeroutput>    </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para>시작 커밋 제목   </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>docs: add text visualizer overview and pipeline analysis</computeroutput>    </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
