<title>6. 집계 명령</title>
<para>대표 집계 명령은 다음과 같다.</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".sh"><codeline><highlight class="normal">git<sp/>rev-list<sp/>--count<sp/>9970ed2009b9650167398ba5fc935a6d94a84f1f^..82f4977551c0034412faf9f17f205f107b73d57a</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">git<sp/>rev-list<sp/>--count<sp/>9970ed2009b9650167398ba5fc935a6d94a84f1f..82f4977551c0034412faf9f17f205f107b73d57a</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">git<sp/>diff<sp/>--numstat<sp/>9970ed2009b9650167398ba5fc935a6d94a84f1f^..82f4977551c0034412faf9f17f205f107b73d57a</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">git<sp/>log<sp/>--numstat<sp/>--format=<sp/>9970ed2009b9650167398ba5fc935a6d94a84f1f^..82f4977551c0034412faf9f17f205f107b73d57a</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para><computeroutput>docs/</computeroutput> 제외 통계는 <computeroutput>awk</computeroutput>에서 path prefix가 <computeroutput>docs/</computeroutput>가 아닌 항목만 합산했다. </para>
</sect1>
